<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٥٩٧ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5509">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ بَشَّارٍ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5532">غُنْدَرٌ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1143">أَبِي بِشْرٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2343">سَعِيدِ بْنِ جُبَيْرٍ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3732">ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ </a>رَضِيَ اللهُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٢٣⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">عَنْهُمَا قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«سُئِلَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> عَنْ أَوْلَادِ الْمُشْرِكِينَ،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ:</span> اللهُ أَعْلَمُ بِمَا كَانُوا عَامِلِينَ.»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>